### Environment Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1

### 1. Get Memory Statistics (Heartbeat)
# Use this endpoint to monitor the current Heap and RSS state
GET {{baseUrl}}/stats
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Trigger Leak: Global Cache
# Execute this multiple times to simulate memory accumulation in the global scope
POST {{baseUrl}}/leak/global-cache
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Clear Memory (Reset)
# This endpoint clears the global cache, allowing the Garbage Collector to reclaim space
POST {{baseUrl}}/leak/clear
Content-Type: application/json